/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt2.log:1881:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:1678:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:11:When `transferFrom(from, uniswapPoolAddress, amount)` is used, the contract spends allowance only for `amount`, then `_transfer` burns an additional `burnAmount` from `from` via `_burn(from, burnAmount)`. Because that extra burn is not covered by `_spendAllowance`, an approved spender can reduce the holder's balance by more than the approved amount.
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt2.log:1882:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:1679:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:19:- The spender calls `transferFrom(holder, uniswapPoolAddress, N)`.
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt2.log:1883:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:1681:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:33:On transfers to `uniswapPoolAddress`, `_transfer` first removes the full `amount` from the sender and credits the recipient with that full `amount`, then separately calls `_burn(from, burnAmount)`. The sender therefore needs enough balance for `amount + burnAmount`, not just `amount`.
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt2.log:1884:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:1682:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:39:- A user with balance `B` calls `transfer(uniswapPoolAddress, B)` or an integration tries to transfer an exact balance to the pool.
