/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt2.log:1886:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Pool-directed_transferFrom_can_burn_more/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:1686:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:75:For transfers to `uniswapPoolAddress`, storage credits the pool with the full `amount` and never credits `marketingWalletAddress`, yet the contract emits events claiming only 97% reached the pool and 2% was sent to the marketing wallet. The event stream therefore misrepresents the actual token movements.
